column7: As Robin I want to have my outputted HTML automatically tagged with RDFa
As Roger I want to use an API to query SPARQL endpoints
As Roger I want to use an API to store and retrieve RDF triples
As Margarete I want to tag my content with minimal distraction
As Robin I want to use existing ontologies (like dbpedia, GoodRelations)
As Margarete I want to easily find related content (by author, date, keyword ...)
As Robin I want to enable page visitors to search for concepts rather than for terms
As Roger I want to serialize RDF graphs in different formats (Trutle, RDF/XML)
As Robin I want to import existing graphs into the local triple store
As Robin I want to map my content objects an properties to existing vocabularies (Person.name -> foaf:name)
As Roger I want to have a schema for URIs to make them dereferencable
